    "description": "Become a father who's helping his family survive in a city overrun by a horde of zombies. Build fortifications in your house, set up traps, and repair the damage caused by ravenous ghouls during attacks on your villa.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Protect your family</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/fbcd8f1cc33e3a09bdfe5d4c122f8945.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/fbcd8f1cc33e3a09bdfe5d4c122f8945.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/fbcd8f1cc33e3a09bdfe5d4c122f8945.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Family comes first. Mind your house and don't let the zombies break into your beloved wife and daughter's room.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Secure the entrances</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/2b2b7c45452f0dc830a5bad2375dfba1.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/2b2b7c45452f0dc830a5bad2375dfba1.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/2b2b7c45452f0dc830a5bad2375dfba1.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Deal with the monsters swiftly and barricade the doors well. Collect construction materials, useful in upgrading the defenses of your stronghold. -Ahem- That is to say, your quaint abode. Make sure all its entrances remain secured, at least for now…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Obtain food and medicine</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/0c7d28a4ca4d775178bb173bf3d5b62f.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/0c7d28a4ca4d775178bb173bf3d5b62f.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/0c7d28a4ca4d775178bb173bf3d5b62f.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Explore the fallen city in search of invaluable food and medicine for your loved ones. You have your trusty car at your disposal, which will help you avoid roving bands of the undead.<br>Find medicine that will help you treat your wounds and your wife's infection. Maybe you'll even manage to resupply on fuel and ammo at your local gas station.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Search the neighborhood</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/7a5bca15d447f8c419a3ce09f94bc80f.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/7a5bca15d447f8c419a3ce09f94bc80f.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/7a5bca15d447f8c419a3ce09f94bc80f.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Investigate the treacherous area and tear through the hellish hordes. Sadly, it seems a local gang has already looted most of the useful and desirable items, including equipment for crafting new weapons among other things.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make new friends</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/3214c5e4d6ee7021ec264c89c095001f.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/3214c5e4d6ee7021ec264c89c095001f.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/3214c5e4d6ee7021ec264c89c095001f.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There are still survivors in nearby houses who will eagerly establish contact you. Help them by assisting with their problems and earn their trust. It might save your life someday…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet local authorities</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/71f6865fab63f73c3b47c0242e689c51.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/71f6865fab63f73c3b47c0242e689c51.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/71f6865fab63f73c3b47c0242e689c51.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The city is under a new law of might set by the local mob. Meet its leader and try to reach some kind of understanding. It is unfortunate that the majority of food and medicine is found inside their storage, where you have no access. This might change if you agree to do some dirty work for these nasty characters, thus gaining a new way to save your family and yourself.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Craft new weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/ec072cae2098c68f3d3f57773ae36a13.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/ec072cae2098c68f3d3f57773ae36a13.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/ec072cae2098c68f3d3f57773ae36a13.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You have a small workshop in your cellar, where you can create new weapons. Ammunition is scarce and you'll have to find alternatives. There's also a small jail there that should provide you with ample opportunity to study the living dead…<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Help the resistance</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/013ad1a143db5d22c2013b97b188fcef.poster.avif?t=1743592305\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/013ad1a143db5d22c2013b97b188fcef.webm?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811350/extras/013ad1a143db5d22c2013b97b188fcef.mp4?t=1743592305\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There is still a group of soldiers clinging to life and trying to fight off the zombies. By helping them, you can get on their good side and maybe, with your forces combined, you'll manage to clean up this city…",
